results.name: Decimal expansion of sqrt(1086).
comment: Continued fraction expansion of sqrt(1086) is 32 followed by (repeat 1, 20, 1, 64).
xref: Cf. A002193 (decimal expansion of sqrt(2)), A002194 (decimal expansion of sqrt(3)), A178231 (decimal expansion of sqrt(181)), A178229 (decimal expansion of (221+11*sqrt(1086))/490).
